@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequence Diagram - US221

actor "Maintenance Supervisor" as SUP
participant "MaintenanceRecordController" as CTRL
participant "MaintenanceReportService" as SVC
participant "MaintenanceRecordRepository" as REPO

SUP -> CTRL : GET /api/maintenance/turnaround-average
activate CTRL

CTRL -> SVC : averageTurnaroundTimePerAircraftType()
activate SVC

SVC -> REPO : findByStatus(COMPLETED)
activate REPO
REPO --> SVC : List<MaintenanceRecord>
deactivate REPO

note right of SVC
  Groups records by aircraft model name.
  For each group, calculates average of
  (endDate - startDate) in days.
end note

SVC --> CTRL : List<TurnaroundAverage>
deactivate SVC

CTRL --> SUP : 200 OK + List<TurnaroundAverageResponse>
deactivate CTRL
@enduml